he parent section title got misplaced onto s6, which only contains a subset of the content. So I'm identifying three section naming issues: s5 and s7 both lack titles, and s6 has been given the parent section's title despite only covering part of that section's content. Additionally, s7 is missing hints for the failure code property names.\n\nFor s6 specifically, while the title \"プロパティファイルの記述ルール\" could work as a breadcrumb showing which top-level section the content belongs to, it's somewhat misleading since the content only addresses a portion of that broader section. I should also verify s8 — the source includes a toctree for sub-documents, but since those are navigation references rather than content, they don't need to be included in the analysis.\n\nI believe I've covered all the issues now and can prepare the final structured output.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":2,"cache_creation_input_tokens":26010,"cache_read_input_tokens":18561,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":26010,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":8},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"d5515830-ce46-4bf3-9530-b393444e9ffa","uuid":"3dba38d6-9fc6-41e7-b284-448b34b7474b"}
